dct_description_sm: Trench map of the area of Ieper, Belgium; relief shown by contours. Contour interval 5 meters. Metric grid. "Strictly confidential." "Issued by Signal Corps, U.S. Army for use in the School of Military Aeronautics"--Ypres area sheet. "Engraved and printed by the U.S. Geological Survey."
